{
    "description_long": "This is a sleek, low-profile red sports car with a streamlined aerodynamic body and a glossy finish. The car features a wide front grille, aggressive headlights, and a sculpted hood with a central air intake. Its side profile reveals large, multi-spoke alloy wheels, pronounced wheel arches, and side air vents for enhanced cooling and performance. The roofline is low and curves smoothly into the rear, which is equipped with a rear window and a subtle integrated spoiler. The rear of the car displays dual exhausts, a central air outlet, and distinctive taillights. The windows are tinted, and the car has two doors, typical of high-performance coupes.",
